instruct the OIC-Municipal Accountant and the Municipal Treasurer to submit to the LSB not later than July 15 of each year the required statement of actual SEF income as basis for the preparation of the Annual LSB budget;
require the Municipal LSB to prepare the SEF budget on or before October 31 of each calendar year to prevent unusual delay in the implementation of primary education PPAs;
