Evaluate the current composition of the MSWMB and look for possible members that could qualify to the required membership thereof; and

Revisit and propose an amendment to the Memorandum of Agreement (MOA) with Econest for the inclusion of the provision on the process of arbitration among the terms and conditions thereof pursuant to Section 59.2 of R.A. No. 9184.

Conduct thorough inspection of the business establishments that are not included in the database of the Municipality to actually validate the existence of the business establishments and their authority to operate;

